author: Bernadette Hughes
text:
Has your municipality developed a Marketing Plan or strategy to attract businesses, consumers, and real estate development?  Whether you developed your plan in-house or utilized external resources, we'd appreciate seeing a copy of your plan, a summary of any actions taken or results, and contact information for the person(s) involved.  Thanks in advance for your assistance.
Bernadette Hughes, Mgmt Analyst
City of Tamarac
title: Municipal Marketing Plan/Strategy
